text: Leane Suniar was an Indonesian archer. She was born on 4 February 1948 and died on 21 November 2021. Suniar competed at the 1976 Summer Olympics.Leane Suniar ManurungLene SUNIAR == References == Category:1948 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Indonesian archers Category:Olympians for Indonesia Category:People from Jakarta
